cs.NI, cs.IT, cs.MM, cs.AR, cs.SY 

The paper discusses the implementation of a channel model for mmWave frequencies in the context of 5G cellular networks, which involves aspects of networking (cs.NI), information theory (cs.IT), multimedia (cs.MM), augmented reality (cs.AR), and systems and control (cs.SY). However, given the focus on network simulation and channel propagation, cs.NI and cs.IT are the most likely categories.
